---
layout: page.njk
title: Economic Development Commission
subtitle: Advising the City Council on strategies to attract, retain, and grow businesses in Aberdeen.
description: Aberdeen Economic Development Commission — business attraction, retention, and economic vitality advisory board.
breadcrumb:
  - label: Boards
    url: /boards/
  - label: Economic Development Commission
---

<div class="grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-10">
  <div class="lg:col-span-2 space-y-8">

    <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">The Economic Development Commission is a citizen advisory board that works to strengthen Aberdeen's business environment. The Commission advises the Mayor and City Council on economic development strategy, business recruitment, and initiatives to promote Aberdeen as a premier business location in the region.</p>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">Commission Focus Areas</h2>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        {% for item in [
          { title: "Business Attraction", desc: "Recruiting new businesses and industries to Aberdeen." },
          { title: "Business Retention", desc: "Supporting and growing existing Aberdeen businesses." },
          { title: "Workforce Development", desc: "Connecting employers with skilled local workers." },
          { title: "Incentive Programs", desc: "Advising on grants, tax incentives, and financing tools." },
          { title: "Downtown Revitalization", desc: "Promoting a vibrant, active commercial downtown." },
          { title: "APG Partnership", desc: "Leveraging Aberdeen Proving Ground for economic opportunity." }
        ] %}
        <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-4">
          <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-navy mb-1">{{ item.title }}</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-600">{{ item.desc }}</p>
        </div>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">Upcoming Meeting</h2>
      {% for meeting in events.meetings %}
      {% if "Economic Development" in meeting.title %}
      <a href="{{ meeting.url }}" class="flex items-center gap-4 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-4 hover:border-gov-blue transition-all duration-200 group">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-navy text-white rounded-lg flex flex-col items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 text-center leading-none">
          <span class="text-xs font-semibold opacity-70 uppercase">{{ meeting.month }}</span>
          <span class="text-2xl font-bold">{{ meeting.day }}</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-sm font-bold text-navy group-hover:text-gov-blue transition-colors duration-200">{{ meeting.title }}</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1">{{ meeting.location }}</div>
        </div>
      </a>
      {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    </div>

    <div class="bg-navy rounded-xl p-6 text-white">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Doing Business in Aberdeen?</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm mb-4">Explore incentives, site selection assistance, and resources available to Aberdeen businesses.</p>
      <a href="{{ '/departments/economic-development/' | url }}" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-gov-blue text-white font-semibold px-5 py-2.5 rounded hover:bg-gov-blue-dark transition-colors duration-200 text-sm">Economic Development Dept.</a>
    </div>

  </div>

  <aside>
    <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-6 sticky top-24 space-y-5">
      <h2 class="text-base font-bold text-navy pb-3 border-b border-slate-100">Contact</h2>
      <dl class="space-y-3 text-sm">
        <div><dt class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1">Phone</dt><dd><a href="tel:+14102721600" class="text-gov-blue hover:underline">(410) 272-1600 ext. 216</a></dd></div>
        <div><dt class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1">Meetings</dt><dd class="text-slate-700">Monthly — Council Chambers</dd></div>
        <div><dt class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1">Address</dt><dd class="text-slate-700">60 N. Parke Street<br/>Aberdeen, MD 21001</dd></div>
      </dl>
      <div class="pt-2 space-y-2">
        <a href="{{ '/departments/economic-development/' | url }}" class="block w-full text-center bg-gov-blue text-white text-sm font-semibold py-2.5 rounded hover:bg-gov-blue-dark transition-colors duration-200">Economic Development</a>
        <a href="{{ '/businesses/' | url }}" class="block w-full text-center border border-slate-200 text-slate-700 text-sm font-semibold py-2.5 rounded hover:border-gov-blue hover:text-gov-blue transition-colors duration-200">Business Resources</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </aside>
</div>
